Welcome
=======
**GOVERNANCE 2.0
BORDERLESS | DECENTRALIZED | VOLUNTARY **

Welcome holons, this is the wiki devoted to the **Bitnation** community. With the participation of the Holons, we want to get people involved to build a true distributed nation.

Create ambassadors and embassies to support the cause of Bitnation or participate in the many chats and forums around the nation.
